 including but not limited to the sale or purchase of the metals by various central banks and financial institutions inflation recession fluctuation in the relative values of the us dollar and foreign currencies particularly the south african rand and russian ruble changes in global and regional demand and political and economic conditions throughout the world the price of palladium is thought to be more closely tied to industrial demand and the rate of underlying world economic growth particularly in automotive production may   c  cybernet data systems inc all rights reserved more from marketwatch more coverage get ready for the lessprofitable amazon that you used to know intel earnings have message for amd and nvidia ‘bring it on’ a case for buying the freakin’ dip with amazon as the mooch might now say most popular all the companies in jeff bezos’s empire in one large chart stock market edges lower on track for weekly losses get ready for the lessprofitable amazon that you used to know intel earnings have message for amd and nvidia ‘bring it on’ how d fullbody scans will change everything from fitness to fashion marketwatch partner center we want to hear from you join the conversation comment sponsored headlines advanced search stocks columns authors topics no results found stillwater mining company nyseswc quotes  news  google financecookies help us deliver our services by using our services you agree to our use of cookieslearn moregot itmy accountsearchmapsyoutubeplaynewsgmaildrivecalendargoogletranslatephotosmoreshoppingwalletfinancedocsbooksbloggercontactshangoutskeepeven more from googlesign inhidden fieldssearch financeadobe flash player is required for interactive charts allowfinancestillwater mining companynyseswcadd to portfoliocompanysummarynewsrelated companieshistorical pricesfinancialsmarketsnewsportfoliosstock screenergoogle domestic trendsrecent quotes  daysyou have no recent quoteschg   stillwater mining company  public nyseswc   watch this stock 