 copper and minor amounts of gold silver and rhodium more from reuters » google finance beta available in hong kong  canada  us  china  ukinformation is provided as is and solely for informational purposes not for trading purposes or advice and may be delayedto see all exchange delays please see disclaimer google  google home  blog  help  report a problem  privacy policy  terms of service stillwater mining company k oct    seeking alphasign in  join nowgo»stillwater mining company swcform k  current reportoct  about stillwater mining company swcview as pdf stillwater mining co de form k received   united states securities and exchange commission washington dc  form k current report pursuant to section  or d of the securities exchange act of  date of report october     date of earliest event reported stillwater mining company exact name of registrant as specified in its charter delaware   state or other jurisdiction of incorporation commission file number irs employer identification no  west dry creek circle suite  littleton co  address of principal executive offices zip code   registrants telephone number including area code not applicable former name or former address if changed since last report check the appropriate box below if the form k filing is intended to simultaneously satisfy the filing obligation of the registrant under any of the following provisions           written communications pursuant to rule  under the securities act  cfr            soliciting material pursuant to rule a under the exchange act  cfr a           precommencement communications pursuant to rule db under the exchange act  cfr db           precommencement communications pursuant to rule ec under the exchange act  cfr ec item  results of operations and financial condition on october   stillwater mining company issued a press release reporting the companys third quarter  results a copy of the press release is attached hereto as exhibit  and is incorporated herein by reference the press 