l montana ore produced from the mines is crushed and concentrated in mills located at each mine site mine concentrates are then trucked to the companys processing complex in columbus montana where they are smelted and partially refined in addition to the mine concentrates the company also recycles spent automotive catalyst and other materials containing pgms it receives from third parties at the processing complex a portion of this recycling activity is material the company purchases for its own account while the remainder is toll processed on behalf of others for a fee after being processed through the companys processing facilities in columbus the final product a pgmrich filter cake is shipped to johnson matthey jm in new jersey for final refining before it is then delivered as finished metal second quarter  summary results for the second quarter of  the company reported a consolidated net income attributable to common stockholders of  million or  per diluted share as compared to the consolidated net loss attributable to common stockholders of  million or  per diluted share for the second quarter of  the lower operating results in the second quarter of  were driven by a significant reduction in average combined realized price per mined ounce which fell from  per ounce in the second quarter of  to  per ounce in the second quarter of  which was offset in part by a reduction in unit costs the second quarter of  included an impairment charge of  million beforetax segment earnings from the companys mining operations totaled  million before income taxes for the second quarter of  compared to  million before income taxes for the same period in  volumes of mined palladium and platinum sold in the second quarter of  increased to  ounces from  ounces in the second quarter of  reflecting both increased production and drawdown of mine ounce inventory the average combined realized price per ounce on sales of mined palladium and platinum in the second quarter of  was  lower tha